thread.title: Chris
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Chris

author: Chris
title: Chris
text: I found Pack & Send to be great. The price was competitive with Australia Post but the delivery was so much faster (2 days instead of Australia Posts 7 working days). I printed the labels off, the package was picked up the same morning and I could track the progress the whole way to delivery. I would highly recommend their service.
